# LLM Quota Data Model

## Schema Definition

```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "LLM Quota Data",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "zai": { "$ref": "#/definitions/provider_quota" },
    "dashscope": { "$ref": "#/definitions/provider_quota" },
    "kimi": { "$ref": "#/definitions/provider_quota" },
    "minimax": { "$ref": "#/definitions/provider_quota" },
    "anthropic": { "$ref": "#/definitions/provider_quota" }
  },
  "definitions": {
    "provider_quota": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "quota_percent": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Remaining quota percentage (0-100)",
          "minimum": 0,
          "maximum": 100
        },
        "usage_percent": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Used quota percentage (0-100)"
        },
        "tokens_used": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Number of tokens used"
        },
        "tokens_limit": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Total token limit"
        },
        "amount_used": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Amount used (for billing-based providers)"
        },
        "amount_limit": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Total amount limit"
        },
        "currency": {
          "type": ["string", "null"],
          "description": "Currency code (e.g., CNY, USD)"
        },
        "remaining_requests": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Remaining API requests"
        },
        "remaining_tokens": {
          "type": ["number", "null"],
          "description": "Remaining tokens (for rate-limited APIs)"
        },
        "reset_at": {
          "type": ["string", "null"],
          "format": "date-time",
          "description": "ISO 8601 timestamp when quota resets"
        },
        "last_checked": {
          "type": "string",
          "format": "date-time",
          "description": "ISO 8601 timestamp of last check"
        },
        "status": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": ["success", "error", "api_accessible", "cached"],
          "description": "Check status"
        },
        "message": {
          "type": ["string", "null"],
          "description": "Error message or additional info"
        },
        "screenshot": {
          "type": ["string", "null"],
          "description": "Path to dashboard screenshot (for browser checks)"
        },
        "dashboard_url": {
          "type": ["string", "null"],
          "format": "uri",
          "description": "URL to provider's dashboard"
        }
      },
      "required": ["status", "last_checked"]
    }
  }
}
```

## Cache Policy

- **TTL**: 1 hour (3600 seconds)
- **Invalidation**: Manual refresh via API endpoint
- **Storage**: `data/quota_data.json`
- **Format**: JSON with UTF-8 encoding

## Alert Thresholds

- **Critical**: < 10% remaining (immediate alert)
- **Warning**: < 20% remaining (notify on next check)
- **Info**: < 50% remaining (log only)

## Provider-Specific Notes

### Z.AI
- Uses 5-hour token cycle + 6-hour cycle
- Returns `percentage` as usage (not remaining)
- Endpoint: `/api/monitor/usage/quota/limit`

### DashScope
- No direct quota API
- Usage tracked via `usage` field in API responses
- Console scraping may be needed for exact quota

### Kimi
- Browser-only access
- Dashboard: `platform.moonshot.cn/dashboard/usage`
- Free tier: 1.5M tokens/day

### MiniMax
- Rate limits: RPM + TPM
- Dashboard: `platform.minimaxi.com/dashboard`
- Check usage in Dashboard → Costs

### Anthropic
- Rate limits via response headers
- 5-hour reset + weekly limits
- Headers: `x-ratelimit-remaining-*`
